{"tid":2077783,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"黨安法就到: 無太空卡，又成日屌正苦既巴絲應該注意以下事項","createTime":"2020-06-24T14:07:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-08T06:22:33.000Z","uid":14918,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"4adfbc7ee0e6653046f3aeeeaaac7e2e239f453b","tid":2077783,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T14:07:42.000Z","msg":"Twitter / IG 文宣帳戶應該用獨立Email登記，不要連繫個人電話號碼，唔好開location tag<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n無太空卡又成日用Telegram/Whatsapp同朋友約行街?<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n試下用Wire 啦<br />\n<br />\nWire好處:<br />\n絕對唔需要用電話號碼開account<br />\n簡單易用，有得multiple login (iOS , Android , PC , Web)<br />\n瑞士公司，Server 係德國、愛爾蘭：受歐盟GDRP保障私人<br />\nApp、server都係開源Open source, 有咩甩漏全世界programer audit<br />\n有第三方安全公司季檢<br />\n<br />\niOS: <a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/app/wire/id930944768?mt=8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fitunes.apple.com%2Fapp%2Fwire%2Fid930944768%3Fmt%3D8&d=Dkz3eIcuz1ZryPyeMF8ZPgomF%2BlBZ%2FxAFwVMru4Rc7Q%3D&h=d2e6327b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://itunes.apple.com/app/wire/id930944768?mt=8</a><br />\nAndroid: <a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.wire&amp;hl=en_US\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Dcom.wire%26hl%3Den_US&d=Dkz3eIcuz1ZryPyeMF8ZPgomF%2BlBZ%2FxAFwVMru4Rc7Q%3D&h=ecaea66c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.wire&amp;hl=en_US</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後 留返條命先可以同土共磨爛蓆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就睇下土共會唔會覺得我地太難處理<br />\n直接係香港整great firewall,繼而再種族滅絕我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ad3f32d183e711624fa91a53097ec6a3a8d38da","tid":2077783,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T14:56:12.000Z","msg":"係咪send mes